Package: MoonDataR
Title: Beginner Tools for Data Exploration and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Anuli", "Segree", email = "anuli.segree@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: MoonDataR is a beginner-friendly R package that helps students
    and new R users explore, clean, summarize, and visualize datasets. The
    package provides simple functions for checking missing values, cleaning
    column names, detecting outliers, creating basic plots, and generating a
    structured S3 data profile object.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    ggplot2
